Three independent AI reviewers (Kimi, ChatGPT, DeepSeek) validated our approach. This isn't marketing fluff - it's [b]peer-reviewed optimization[/b].

[b]4. Quantum-Resistant Future-Proofing[/b]
Post-quantum cryptography (Dilithium5, Kyber1024, AEGIS-QL) protects against quantum computers that will break Bitcoin by 2030-2035.

[b]5. Performance-Agnostic Tokenomics[/b]
Time-based halving enables us to optimize sync speed [b]without affecting emission schedule[/b]. Improve 100x? Tokenomics stay identical.

[b]6. True Decentralization[/b]
P2P libp2p networking, no centralized servers, Tor integration for anonymity. TurboSync makes decentralization [b]fast AND reliable[/b].

[b]7. Open Source & Transparent[/b]
All code is Apache 2.0 licensed. Full technical documentation. Security through cryptography, not obscurity.

